Vehement/Dark One:




Vehement watched as FZ landed, looking to Dark One.

"That is our leader." Dark One said, looking to FZ, not knowing that wasn't 
the real Zardus, but Future Zardus.  "Zardus, this is Vehement, leader of 
this ship.  He wishes to negotiate a tribute so he may stay alive."
